reviewText: The condition of the item was perfect though London has Fallen is a better flcik

Loved this movie when I first saw it, so I had to find it! Nobody around me had carried it, so I was glad I could turn to Amazon!! It came in great shape, no scratches, cracks, etc... it was a family hit, adult wise! If you haven't seen this movie, I highly recommend!
Great DVD.  Full of action and is fast-paced.  Good for a night in with popcorn.  Probably not great for kids of younger ages due to violence and language.
Farfetched??? Maybe not in today's tech. Entertaining in the least.
A favorite of mine. Definitely a great purchase. If you haven't seen this movie, I highly recommend you do.
